Revision history for Syndicate

{{$NEXT}}

    - Complete rewrite of original p6-syndication

    [Core architecture]
    - Add Syndicate::Extensions registry for decoupled extension
      parsing/generation (MediaRSS, DublinCore, ITunes)
    - Extract Syndicate::RSS::Common role to deduplicate image, textinput,
      skipHours, skipDays logic between RSS 2.0 and V0_91
    - Thicken Syndicate::Feed role with $.generator and $.language
    - Thicken Syndicate::Item role with $.id and $.content
    - Standardize extension naming: iTunes → ITunes (CamelCase)

    [Formats]
    - Add RSS 0.91 parsing and generation
    - Add RSS 1.0 (RDF) parsing and generation
    - Add Atom 1.0 full XML output with all fields and entity handling
    - Add JSON Feed 1.1 parsing and generation
    - Add feed discovery via HTML <link> tag scanning

    [API]
    - Add Syndicate::Builder::Feed / Syndicate::Builder::Entry for
      format-agnostic feed construction
    - Add Syndicate.parse, feed-format, parse-feed unified API
    - Add builder ↔ feed data sync for role attributes

    [Extensions]
    - Add iTunes podcast extension (itunes:author, itunes:summary,
      itunes:duration)
    - Add Media RSS extension (media:content, media:thumbnail,
      media:title, media:description)
    - Add Dublin Core extension (dc:creator, dc:date, dc:subject)

    [Docs & Packaging]
    - Comprehensive README with usage guide and API reference
    - POD documentation on all 23 modules
    - Register missing modules in META6.json provides (Syndicate::Extensions,
      Syndicate::RSS::Common, Syndicate::Extension::ITunes)
    - Full test suite (13 files, 483 assertions) covering parsing,
      generation, roundtrip, builder, discovery, concurrency, and
      extensions
